}

### Preferences/My - Kullanıcı tercihlerini getir (yoksa oluşturur)
POST {{BaseUrl}}/Preferences/My
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

### Preferences/Update - Kullanıcı tercihlerini güncelle
POST {{BaseUrl}}/Preferences/Update
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "preferredCountryCode": "TR",
    "preferredCurrency": "TRY",
    "timezone": "Europe/Istanbul"
}
